item.title: ICURFC 2nd XV’s winning streak lives on
item.author: Gustave RDB,
item.description: Imperial 2nd XV 20 - 7 UCL 3rd XV On Wednesday, freshers discovered the pleasure of taking public transport to Fortress Harlington for our second game of the season. It was nice to see that the other team actually showed up on time after the 40-minute game last week. After a quick but intense and …
